UID:79b8fe5e61a9e70f86c4893bee277df941eaf726@macro-calendar.local
DTSTAMP:20260528T170934Z
DTSTART:20260612T180000Z
DTEND:20260612T190000Z
SUMMARY:🔥 US Fed: FOMC Interest Rate Decision + Summary of Economic Pr
 ojections
DESCRIPTION:Source: US Fed\nImpact: high\nFOMC scheduled meeting decision
  day. Time assumed as 2:00pm New York unless confirmed otherwise.\n\nExp
 lainer:\n• What it is: Central Bank Rate Decision\n\n• Measures: Int
 erest-rate decision\, policy statement and guidance from the central ban
 k.\n\n• Usual market effect: More hawkish-than-expected guidance is us
 ually bullish for the local currency and bearish for bonds. More dovish-
 than-expected guidance is usually bearish for the currency and bullish f
 or bonds.\n\n• Why traders care: Central-bank decisions directly affec
 t interest rates\, currency valuation\, bond yields and equity risk appe
 tite.\n\n• Frequency: Scheduled several times per year.\n\n• Notes: 
 The market often reacts not only to the rate decision\, but also to the 
 statement\, forecasts\, press conference and tone.\n\n• Acronyms: FOMC
  = Federal Open Market Committee\; RBA = Reserve Bank of Australia.\n\nO
 fficial source: https://www.federalreserve.gov/monetarypolicy/fomccalend
 ars.htm
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-PT24H
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Tomorrow: 🔥 US Fed: FOMC Interest Rate Decision + Summary 
 of Economic Projections
END:VALARM
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-PT30M
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:30 minutes: 🔥 US Fed: FOMC Interest Rate Decision + Summar
 y of Economic Projections
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT
